Q: how to delete all messages with "mathgroup" in the "To:" field?
A: well...
        ^T
            Untag messages matching: .
        T
            Tag messages matching: ~C mathgroup
                (means mathgroup is in To: or cc:)
        ;d  (; means "for all tagged things do")
        $   (synchronize)

  apparently '/' searches in subject?

Q: how to toggle view-by-thread?
A:
        :set sort=date
        :set sort=threads


Q: how to view/save attachments?
       v to view attachments
